snippet.title: Golden Sails Gameplay Preview
snippet.description:
A short video recorded from the current version of Golden Sails, an upcoming naval Life Sim game where you manage your crew and fend off enemy ships while adventuring across the seas. 
Demo releasing publicly in February 2025
